<title>Community</title>
<h1>Community</h1>

<p>Vote Squared was founded by Forest Handford.  We welcome help from the international community to broaden Vote Squared's reach.  RateMyGovernment.ca joined the Vote Squared site in 2015.  Every country with is welcome to have content here.  While we may not understand your country's needs, we are open to helping you contribute to Vote Squared to meet those needs.</p>

<p>The software behind Vote Squared is open source.  You may contribute to the code via <a href="https://github.com/ForestJay/VoteSquared">pull requests on GitHub</a>. </p>

<p>As a social platform, users are encouraged to add content to the site.  This content can include adding politicians, updating politician information, and rating politicians.</p>

